        "executionPlatformVersion": "1.3"
        }</zeebe:userTaskForm>
      <zeebe:userTaskForm id="userTaskForm_0uce7gn">{
        "components": [
        {
        "text": "# Add Links to the Release Notification E-Mail Template\nAll release managers are
        requested to share information about their release to the Release Notification Email
        Template for the upcoming release in the Drive Google Drive folder [Release
        Notifications](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1hziaQOP3vzshJicigEY5ME4BFj--ObYV?usp=sharing)\n\n\n1.
        Blog post links as soon as they are available\n2. Release notes aka Change Log \n\n",
        "type": "text",
        "id": "Field_0y14qts"
        }
        ],
        "schemaVersion": 4,
        "exporter": {
        "name": "Camunda Web Modeler",
        "version": "e73c95f"
        },
        "type": "default",
        "id": "add-links-to-email",
        "executionPlatform": "Camunda Cloud",
        "executionPlatformVersion": "1.3"
        }</zeebe:userTaskForm>
      <zeebe:userTaskForm id="userTaskForm_2doapka">{
        "components": [],
        "schemaVersion": 4,
        "exporter": {
        "name": "Camunda Web Modeler",
        "version": "24b59bc"
        },
        "type": "default",
        "id": "release-download-page",
        "executionPlatform": "Camunda Cloud",
        "executionPlatformVersion": "1.3"
        }</zeebe:userTaskForm>
      <zeebe:userTaskForm id="userTaskForm_3nralv7">{
        "components": [
        {
        "text": "# Update List of Old Releases and Last Release\nIf you have not done so already in
        Phase 1, add your Release to the [List of old
        Releases](https://confluence.camunda.com/display/CO/Optimize+Release+Overview). Also, update
        the Last releases done by developer section with your release.",
        "type": "text",
        "id": "Field_0y14qts"
        }
        ],
        "schemaVersion": 4,
        "exporter": {
        "name": "Camunda Web Modeler",
        "version": "e73c95f"
        },
        "type": "default",
        "id": "update-release-list",
        "executionPlatform": "Camunda Cloud",
        "executionPlatformVersion": "1.3"
        }</zeebe:userTaskForm>
      <zeebe:userTaskForm id="userTaskForm_3ghn0p2">{
        "components": [
        {
        "text": "# Hand the Release Token\n1. Hand the [Release
        Token](https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/marvelcinematicuniverse/images/2/25/Mjolnir.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/1000?cb=20140129001244)
        to the next Release Manager,\n2. [Assign the new release
        manager](https://confluence.camunda.com/display/CO/Update+the+Optimize+Release+Manager+Role+in+Slack)
        to the optimize-release-manager user group on Slack. The next release manager can be found
        by checking out the [last releases done by developer
        section](https://confluence.camunda.com/display/CO/Optimize+Release+Overview) and picking
        the developer that has done the release procedure the longest time ago.",
        "type": "text",
        "id": "Field_0y14qts"
        }
        ],
        "schemaVersion": 4,
        "exporter": {
        "name": "Camunda Web Modeler",
        "version": "e73c95f"
        },
        "type": "default",
        "id": "token-handover",
        "executionPlatform": "Camunda Cloud",
        "executionPlatformVersion": "1.3"
        }</zeebe:userTaskForm>
